_sText:
[Map demonstration video.](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6Ud44UXx8bk "Map demonstration video.")

An open space map that can be played in AIM matches, 1v1 play or Gun Game.

It features several teleporters and boost pads to warp and fling the player across the map. From the main platforms, a sniper platform can be accessed which has a teleporter to a healing zone.

This map has a proper soundscape and a custom skybox.
